des: Gujarat is a flourishing state with cultural diversity. This vibrant state forms an integral part of the Indian culture. Gujarati culture is the blend of traditions, beliefs, customs, arts, values and modernization. Despite of being among the most industrialized state India, Gujarat preserves its rich culture and tradition of the ancient past.
